The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Veerans tame Lions 3-0

Chandigarh: Services striker Suresh Kumar dished out a scintillating performance and found an able ally in skipper Adam Sinclair and Spanish import Albert Casas, as Chennai Veerans upset Bangalore Lions 3-0 in a PHL match on Tuesday. 

Chennai took the lead in the 14th minute through Suresh and Adam. 

Two minutes later, Suresh did the spadework. 

Chennai rounded off the tally in the last minute of the third quarter with Suresh himself finding the target. 

Suresh was adjudged Lion-Of-The-Match. 

